section.section:
The criteria shall include:
The qualifying strategic characteristics of the property, including location and productivity;
The circumstances creating the risk of the property being sold for nonagricultural purposes;
When applicable, the characteristics of the purchaser of strategic farmland seeking assistance from the Program;
The consistency of the proposed acquisition with county goals and priorities and, if applicable, the county's priority preservation area; and
Evaluation of the property as a priority easement acquisition.
